To run the program to find and identify the cluedo character:

1) In the folder that this file is saved in, there is a folder called 'Input_Points'. Copy the input points for the world into this folder and call the file "input_points.yaml"

2) In the singularity, execute the following commands:

	pip install --user imutils
	xterm&

3) In the Xterm window that appears, navigate to the group_project folder and execute:

	rosrun project Cluedo_Solver_new.py

The picture of the green cicle, the picture of the poster and the text file containing the name of the identified character will be saved in the "Project_Output" folder
